sigma_analysis_results.rule_description: Detects the use of PowerShell to identify the current logged user.

match_context.values:
@{ScriptBlockText=
        $Action = New-ScheduledTaskAction -Execute "C:\Users\george\AppData\Roaming\Microsoft\Windows\Applications\Runtime Broker.exe"

        $Principal = New-ScheduledTaskPrincipal -UserId $env:USERNAME -LogonType Interactive

        $Settings = New-ScheduledTaskSettingsSet -AllowStartIfOnBatteries -DontStopIfGoingOnBatteries -DontStopOnIdleEnd
